ok so once again im at the point where im thinking "what the fuck am i doing to myself?" and ive decided i have to settle down and chill out for a while, just to let myself recover. I had a job interview for assistant manager with bevilles on thursday and i got a second interview for monday. im really nervous thinking about it because i would like so much to get the job because its in werribee which will cut my petrol bill down by about 50 bucks a week and its a payrise to what im on now. the bad thing is i know my boss is going to be really stuck if i leave and i feel disloyal to them for leaving in the way i will be if i get the job. im not letting myself think about it too much because im still a long way from having the position.

went out last weekend with nikki nick and the boys. sam was there and he kept staring at me, still cant work out why i always have guys that just stare, its really weird. anyway he made an apology saying sorry for being such an asshole but i didnt have a bar of it, just shrugged him off. i dont care now. so they left early and we ended up going to amber lounge and had a good dance, it was cool. 

didnt do much this week, been trying to get off the bongs again but its sooo much harder this time. i cant believe how easily i fell back into it. i had quit for only about 2 months i think and already its fucked up, so yeh been smoking every night and feeling really guilty about it. i dont need this shit on my brain so tonight is the last night, next week is a fresh new week to be happy healthy and hard working for a change. i wish myself luck!
